_sText:
Thanks for taking a look at my map.
This map contains darkness, rain and lightning, these include the sounds to go accordingly.
This map also has 1 secret room which is triggered by a button. Good luck finding it :)

I would just like to point out that this is my first ever map, please if you are going to criticize, do it constructively.

Map should be place in Steam\steamapps\usernamehere\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

There are also 2 custom decals used, these should be placed in:
Steam\steamapps\usernamehere\counter-strike source\cstrike\materials\decals

Thanks for downloading :)
